Package: kumquat
Title: A Smaller Version of LIME 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Janith", "Wanniarachchi", , "janithcwanni@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: The existing implementation LIME can be quite limiting in understanding the underlying components that make LIME work. kumquat is a simpler implementation of LIME that is easier to understand and is more transparent on the pieces that come together to make LIME work.
